Package Maths

Class ManhattanKNN

  • java.lang.Object
    • Maths.kNN
      • Maths.MinkowskiKNN
        • Maths.ManhattanKNN

  • public class ManhattanKNN
extends MinkowskiKNN
    Maths.ManhattanKNN extends the Maths.kNN abstract method and uses an Manhattan distance metric for the calculations. The formula is [distance] = sum(endPoint - origin) where the sum adds the values for every dimension.
    Version:
    Milestone 4
    Author:
    Darren
